{"tid":889992,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果 跌破 1萬億元市值","createTime":"2018-11-05T03:34:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T01:34:31.000Z","uid":66351,"like":58,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"63040bf8aaab820a117859bc5b4c91537f727649","tid":889992,"uid":66351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T03:34:36.000Z","msg":"蘋果公司業績展望黯淡且<span style=\"color: red;\">不再公布iPhone銷量</span>，拖累蘋果股價2日重挫逾6%，並跌至修正領域，市值面臨1兆美元保衛戰，也讓寄望蘋果財報能提振科技股行情的投資人大失所望。投資大師<span style=\"color: red;\">巴菲特</span>所領導的波克夏公司也因此遭遇單日帳面損失近40億美元。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果2日收盤大跌6.6%至每股207.48美元，創2014年1月來最大單日跌幅。若依蘋果最新公布的在外流通股數計算，蘋果目前市值仍略高於1兆美元，但如果扣除上季已實施庫藏股所買回的在外流通股股數，這次大跌讓蘋果市值蒸發約860億美元，市值因此萎縮至9,870億美元，<span style=\"color: red;\">跌破兆美元大關</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f8a1addfcc47b672d6d09745f6e3d5e58cb14f","tid":889992,"uid":12449,"like":6,"dislike":117,"score":-111,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T03:35:58.000Z","msg":"美國大公司連人工島都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18b9947afe0250fe110ba001a16428dcdf8af37","tid":889992,"uid":80481,"like":151,"dislike":1,"score":150,"quote":{"pid":"08f8a1addfcc47b672d6d09745f6e3d5e58cb14f","tid":889992,"uid":12449,"like":6,"dislike":117,"score":-111,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T03:35:58.000Z","msg":"美國大公司連人工島都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T03:36:42.000Z","msg":"一萬億係美元啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896200bea77d2dd83a36aa1d8b05fbe8f0c0fc1b","tid":889992,"uid":22999,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08f8a1addfcc47b672d6d09745f6e3d5e58cb14f","tid":889992,"uid":12449,"like":6,"dislike":117,"score":-111,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T03:35:58.000Z","msg":"美國大公司連人工島都不如<img src=\"/a